# .git-blame-ignore-revs
#
# Revisions listed here are skipped by `git blame` so that large,
# purely-mechanical commits (formatting-only, no behavior change) don't
# obscure the real authorship of each line.
#
# Enable locally with:
#   git config blame.ignoreRevsFile .git-blame-ignore-revs
# (GitHub honors this file automatically.)
#
# Per the codebase cleanup plan (plan_ext.md §5.1 / Phase 3), the single
# repo-wide `prettier --write` reformat is deferred until AFTER the god-file
# splits land, so its diff never collides with move diffs. When that commit
# ships, add its full 40-char SHA below (one per line, with a short comment).
#
